This is a score keeper for Least Count card game. Requires Python2.6 and bash. It does not work with Python3. There is a gtk version as well as a commandline version. Only the commandline version currently supports saving states.

To run program for first time:

	$python least-count-scorer.py

To restore a saved game state :

	$python least-count-scorer.py [saved-game-name]

Visit http://rr0hit.wordpress.com/2011/05/21/a-simple-python-score-keeper-for-least-count-card-game/for the game rules.
